--- Astrotrain ---

Astrotrain homes in on Spasstik's signal, and comes out of the lower 
atmopshere. He plummets downward at an alarming rate. At about 7000 
feet, as he nears 333 meters per second, he pulls up, causing a 
sonic boom to emminate around the surrounding area. Breaking, he 
levels off near ground level. He quickly transforms into train mode, 
and lands on the ground, continuing onward. He matches speed with 
Spasstik, and his side door slides open. "Spasstik, in, NOW." He 
continues to match speed with Spasstik, but he won't be able to for 
long.
